snippet.title: Ghost Does Things - Symposium of Grief
snippet.description:
A video about Ghost, from 'Symposium of Grief,' doing things. Just general things. 

If you want to see Ghost do those things and more, play the game here: https://t-dogextreme.itch.io/symposium-of-grief

This trailer showcases footage from an unreleased patch, so hold up your socks for that oncoming blessing.
